  <name>OneKey Wallet</name>
  <summary>All-in-one crypto wallet with hardware support</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>LicenseRef-proprietary=https://github.com/OneKeyHQ/app-monorepo/blob/x/LICENSE.md</project_license>
  <description>
    <p>This is the official Flatpak build of OneKey Wallet, packaged from the upstream AppImage.</p>
    <p>OneKey is an all-in-one wallet for managing and trading crypto assets with built-in hardware wallet support.</p>
    <p>Use PC/SC to connect hardware wallets; ensure the PCSC daemon is available on the host for device access inside the sandbox. Bridge/HTTP flows remain available over the granted network/ipc sockets.</p>
  </description>
